layout.p:
Columns: 2;
                                                  ruled lines: 25;
                                                  written lines: 25; Uniform layout. Pencil ruling and occasionally pricking is visible. Chronicles and Esther begin a new column, and Proverbs opens a new leaf. If there is not sufficient room in a line to complete the last word, the final letter or the last two letters of the same word are placed in the margin, some vacant space being left between the columns and these letters. The number of Psalms is 151 (number 96 is divided into two parts). Few masoretic notes.
